## ðŸ“Š Ranking & Evaluation Model (APERA)

Algo Odyssey uses **APERA (Adaptive Plagiarism-aware Efficiency-based Ranking Algorithm)** which evaluates submissions based on:

* âœ… Correctness (test case pass rate)
* â± Execution time
* ðŸ“ˆ Time & space complexity (inferred)
* ðŸ“š Historical performance
* ðŸš« Plagiarism score
* ðŸ•’ Timely participation

This ensures **fair, adaptive, and industry-aligned rankings** rather than brute-force scoring.

